data.description: *****OPEN HOUSE SATURDAY Jan 20,2024 from  12 -3pm **** SELLER'S OFFERING $5000 TOWARDS CLOSING COSTS*****Come check out this Stunning 5 bedroom, 3.5 bath Chesmar Home build nestled in the highly desireable & gated community of The Terraces at Alamo Ranch.  This Gorgeous Home welcomes you with a Beautiful Entryway. The Home features a grand 2-story entry highlighting rot iron 2nd floor banister, an open layout, natural light flows & hard wood floors throughout living areas!  Formal Dining room, two living areas, spacious kitchen & breakfast nook.  The kitchen sports electric cooktop, built-in oven, granite countertops, breakfast bar, GE appliances, plenty of storage with 42' cabinets & so much more.  Master bedroom located on the 1st floor, with other bedrooms upstairs, ceiling fans throughout. UPSTAIRS: 2nd living area/game room, 2 Bedrooms share a jack and jill bathroom, 5th bedroom/office. This home offers an oversized, approx 20 ft high 2.5-car garage. NEW AC (replaced Oct 2023) & NEW Water Heaters (replaced Aug 2023).  Water softener! In ground sprinkler system,  fully landscape, with large backyard, gorgeous large live oaks providing front/backyard shade, covered patio & pergola sitting on large stones for outdoor entertainment with electrical outlet for TV or outdoor lighting.  No Back Neighbors!! Neighborhood amenities located within the gates.  With easy access to all Major highways, NISD schools, walking distance to Elementry, HEB, restaurants, coffee shop & close proximity to shopping centers, SeaWorld, Fiesta Texas & Lackland AFB. Do not miss the chance to make this your dream home.  Call now to schedule a private tour!
